reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect in so many ways
reviews.reviewText: “Dishwasher Magnet Clean Dirty Sign Non-Scratch Strong Clean Dirty Magnet Modern Silver Strong Slide for Changing Signs Easy to Read Farmhouse Rustic Wood Design Kitchen Accessories for Dishwasher“This magnetic dishwasher sign is perfect. The silver colored mat finish matches the exterior of our stainless steel Bosch dishwasher very well.The magnet holds the sign strongly in place, so it doesn’t move around at all when you open or close the dishwasher door. Plus, the magnet is covered by a plastic panel, so it won’t scratch the stainless steel surface if somebody does happen to slide the sign around on the door.The panel that you slide back and forth to reveal the “Dirty” or “Clean” message slides smoothly, but it stays in place to whichever side you move it to. Plus, the wording is acrylic, and the sign itself is plastic, so it cleans easily and it won’t rust.The sign is larger than it looks in the photos (7” x 2”), but it looks great on our dishwasher. $5.99 is a bargain.
